metadata.name: Kenopsia
metadata.description:
Kenopsia (Ken-op-sia) is the sad feeling of a place that was usually full or once full but now is abandoned and quiet.


Feelings are what that makes us human, but there are some feelings in life that we know and are able to feel but unable to express in words. This series will help you in discovering those feelings which we feel but can't tell through my images embracing the sweet melancholy


Artist - Ritam Bhattacharya
Genre - Landscape Photography
Edition - 1/1
Place - Coorg, India
